OL,3,CMapped: The best and worst councils
OL,4,Cfor pothole repairs
OL,6,FA new traffic-light rating system has
OL,7,Frevealed which councils in England are
OL,8,Ffixing potholes well - and which are
OL,9,Ffalling behind.
OL,11,FThe new mapping tool by the Department
OL,12,Ffor Transport (DfT) shows 154 local
OL,13,Fhighway authorities rated as red,
OL,14,Famber or green based on road
OL,15,Fconditions and how effectively they
OL,16,Fare spending the government's road
OL,17,Fmaintenance funding.
OL,19,FThis means drivers are now able to see
OL,20,Fhow well their local authority is
OL,21,Ftackling potholes.
